{"tid":2499831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"運輸工涉藏螺絲批及鐵蓮花等 今被裁定三項控罪罪名成立 還押至5月6日判刑","createTime":"2021-04-22T07:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:48:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6487783ace4153a002129524adeb2091c0e5846f","tid":2499831,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15200&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=3379c13c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15200</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第五庭 <br />\n#劉綺雲裁判官 <br />\n#1208灣仔 #裁決 <br />\n<br />\n👤陳(27) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)管有適合作非法用途的工具並有所意圖<br />\n(2)管有攻擊性武器並有所意圖<br />\n(3)管有違禁武器 <br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n於2019年12月8日，在灣仔柯布連道與告士打道交界，攜有各一螺絲批(控罪一) 、一把刀連套(控罪二) 及指節套(控罪三) 。 <br />\n<br />\n裁決速報<br />\n裁判官信納PW1-7證供，不接納被告的作供。<br />\n裁定被告三項控罪罪名成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n被告需要還押至 5月6日 1430 判刑，其間索取背景報告。"},{"pid":"29ec1f35737231f857e07888eb8ed433515902e8","tid":2499831,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e8172e0de0c5630f84112a144d57a5a203cc9c","tid":2499831,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"有指節套就真係過份左"},{"pid":"96a0f573b8025a72e0687fd0ffe954f969a2b01c","tid":2499831,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbd4d055eaf395071a8f826bb8a3cc4689cf58b","tid":2499831,"uid":95059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfbffa6d9f3150dc6b8761e552db2eddbd7fdd5","tid":2499831,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e8172e0de0c5630f84112a144d57a5a203cc9c","tid":2499831,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"有指節套就真係過份左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"指節套係咩?<br />\n鐵蓮花?"},{"pid":"387bf5d72ee3181ee18017664ff9852a178d3f9c","tid":2499831,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cfbffa6d9f3150dc6b8761e552db2eddbd7fdd5","tid":2499831,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e8172e0de0c5630f84112a144d57a5a203cc9c","tid":2499831,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"有指節套就真係過份左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"指節套係咩?<br />\n鐵蓮花?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:00:17.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"75b1ee4dbcda30b65d17413c84de071ee75f8599","tid":2499831,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4078b493fe0cc22ed04abef565a76b280a5e2f01","tid":2499831,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4766794c4ec9fa46ae13c0ea763cf1089accc774","tid":2499831,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"他稱一直與警員合作，打算向警員解釋行山刀是買給朋友，惟其間突有一名<span class=\"red\">手持雷明燈槍的警員行近並大聲質問</span>謂：「啲刀喺咪用嚟捅我同事？」由於他感到緊張，故沒再向警員解釋詳情。至於涉案鐵指環，被告解釋是鎖匙扣裝飾，由朋友六年前贈送。<br />\n<br />\n劉官又指，被告聲稱行山刀是新買，卻在半年後才向店員查詢有沒有收據；對方答沒有，故被告未能提供單據。劉官不同意被告說法，認為<span class=\"red\">被告被捕後預計有法律風險，理應致電向店方查詢</span>，有關證據卻完全欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n至於被告稱當時有警員大聲質問，故此才沒向警員說出行山刀是買給朋友的詳情，劉官亦不認為<span class=\"red\">警員會做出影響同袍查問工作的舉動</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買啲野有預計有風險所以要拎單據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/Q6ZUQP3DGVG3FKNM7QWDKRS7FU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FQ6ZUQP3DGVG3FKNM7QWDKRS7FU%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=5a01c2c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FQ6ZUQP3DGVG3FKNM7QWDKRS7FU%2F&h=50ac76e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/Q6ZUQP3DGVG3FKNM7QWDKRS7FU/</a>"},{"pid":"b9f6328fae7e7524a8ee01c6ed8de0bd555c315f","tid":2499831,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"官：被告說法既不合情理亦不可信<br />\n<br />\n裁判官直言，被告的證供不可信，亦不可靠。被問到未有提供收據的原因時，被告稱是<span class=\"red\">因警方沒有要求</span>。裁判官認為，被告答案明顯<span class=\"red\">迴避問題、砌詞狡辯</span>，她指在截查時，行山刀及螺絲批均沒有包裝顯示為新購置的，若被告不告知警方，警方便無法得知，故被告不能將責任歸咎於警方。就被告聲稱受驚後不敢發言，裁判官則指，若被告如自辯所稱的主動配合截查，<span class=\"red\">警員並不會無緣無故上前質問他，妨礙同袍進行調查</span>，因此認為其說法不合情理，不接納其開脫理由。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官續稱，被告聲稱因疫情甚少外出，在案發 6 個月後才查詢購買涉案行山刀及螺絲批的店鋪，惟對方表示已沒有該收據記錄。裁判官指，被告以擔心疫情為由，沒有即時以電話或其他方法聯絡店鋪，索取對自己有利的證據，實屬有違常理。而對被告走往金鐘方向，裁判官亦指，考慮到當下的心理、生理狀態，<span class=\"red\">認為被告理應選擇路程較短，遠離人流的路線往天后方向離開，以避免突發事件，而非往金鐘方向前行</span>。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B5%E8%93%AE%E8%8A%B1%E7%AD%89-%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5-3-%E7%BD%AA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%85%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91-%E5%AE%98-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5-3-%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=659ddcf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5-3-%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%2F&h=273cb1d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B5%E8%93%AE%E8%8A%B1%E7%AD%89-%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5-3-%E7%BD%AA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%85%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91-%E5%AE%98-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警唔介入, 車輪咁問你都試過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1584dddd972a120f11975c708b860855399d21c","tid":2499831,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c1043746ce303bb95b3bc1597e82e6ac38a6bb","tid":2499831,"ui